content: Very hard to put your face on we got folks that start really fast and then some that take the full 6 months to ramp up, but end up being in our top 10% of sales reps. And so - rather you pay more attention to the net new areas, which is what I commented on this quarter the first quarters where just wanted to give you all some color on how many reps it took to get to the 23 net new areas.
